                  "pageId": 1488041,
                  "revisionId": 2694197,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "This mod will make projectiles stop when hitting energy orbs, potentially wasting ammo. This can vary with hitscan weapons."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Energizing Shot",
                  "pageId": 1488041,
                  "revisionId": 2694197,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Weapons with Multishot can pick up energy orbs with just a single pellet/projectile."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Energizing Shot",
                  "pageId": 1488041,
                  "revisionId": 2694197,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Energy orbs picked up this way will trigger on-Energy-pickup effects, like Arcane Energize , Energy Conversion , Equilibrium and Zenurik 's Energy Pulse bonus regeneration."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Energizing Shot",
                  "pageId": 1488041,
                  "revisionId": 2694197,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Zenurik's Energy Pulse scales off of the increased energy gained, while Equilibrium (including Equinox 's passive) does not ."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Energizing Shot",
                  "pageId": 1488041,
                  "revisionId": 2694197,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Bonus does affect Equilibrium 's conversion on Energy Orbs from dispensers in Arena gamemodes."
                }
              },
              {
